content:
To add Apple Pay to an enhanced Apple Messages for Business channel:

Set up Apple Pay in your Apple settings.

Add your merchant information to your Messages for Business account.

Import your merchant identity certificate into your Salesforce sandbox.

Update your Messaging channel settings by adding Apple Pay and selecting the imported Merchant Identity Certificate.

Verify your merchant domain with Apple.

Create an Apex class to process payments using the ProcessPaymentHandler Interface as a guide.

Create a payment messaging component, Apex classes, and flow that agents can use in messaging sessions.
title: Setting up Apple Pay in Service Cloud
